00:02:06.899 --> 00:02:08.211
not create them.

00:02:08.937 --> 00:02:12.574
So this issue became very personal to me.

00:02:13.011 --> 00:02:15.693
I said, "You know what?
We have to solve this."

00:02:15.717 --> 00:02:20.414
And we can, with some of the existing
systems we already have in place.

00:02:21.289 --> 00:02:24.512
